318
00:14:56,384 --> 00:14:58,271
♪Seas transform into fields♪

319
00:14:58,523 --> 00:15:04,538
♪No foe outweighs love's pristine sheen♪

320
00:15:05,807 --> 00:15:07,621
♪Tracing every breath you take in vain♪

321
00:15:07,817 --> 00:15:12,040
