322
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:12,680
It's over.

323
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:14,680
It's over.

324
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:16,960
Everything's in the past.

325
00:15:16,980 --> 00:15:19,424
♪A lifetime's devotion never wavers♪

326
00:15:19,424 --> 00:15:23,668
♪All for you, forever due♪

327
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,960
(Wange.)

328
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:55,280
(I'm your father!)

329
00:15:55,280 --> 00:15:56,560
(You can't do this to me!)

330
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,960
(Forgive me. It's all my fault.)

331
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:02,040
(No!)

332
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:10,480
Hello?

333
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:12,720
Can't sleep?

334
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:15,640
How did you know?

335
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:19,680
I'm now at your doorstep.

336
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,480
I see your lights are still on.

337
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:25,640
It's okay.

338
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,080
I won't hang up.

339
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:28,720
Don't be scared.

340
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:31,360
Sleep peacefully.

341
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,440
I'll stay right here.

342
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:40,440
Okay.

343
00:16:43,604 --> 00:16:48,539
♪Watching the hour hand in slow motion♪

344
00:16:50,419 --> 00:16:55,507
♪How ironic to think I was foolproof♪

345
00:16:57,230 --> 00:17:02,157
