346
00:17:02,739 --> 00:17:08,836
♪When you've deleted me from your heart♪

347
00:17:09,043 --> 00:17:10,931
♪The cruelest distance♪

348
00:17:10,995 --> 00:17:13,331
♪It's you in my memories♪

349
00:17:13,395 --> 00:17:15,840
♪Walking towards tomorrow♪

350
00:17:15,891 --> 00:17:17,683
♪Nostalgia is ongoing♪

351
00:17:17,779 --> 00:17:22,547
♪Because we can't alter the ending♪

352
