♪The most intimate distance♪

353
00:17:24,467 --> 00:17:29,262
♪It's once done, now past♪

354
00:17:29,692 --> 00:17:35,827
♪You're clearly in every breath I take♪

355
00:17:36,262 --> 00:17:39,379
♪Yet drifting away♪

356
00:17:41,812 --> 00:17:42,852
I'm returning this to you.

357
00:17:56,732 --> 00:17:58,012
