358
00:17:59,692 --> 00:18:01,412
just to get back at Zhou Nian?

359
00:18:06,092 --> 00:18:07,372
Then my second question.

360
00:18:08,652 --> 00:18:10,332
Did you help drive Zhou Nian

361
00:18:11,972 --> 00:18:12,772
