364
00:18:20,812 --> 00:18:22,852
How I feel is irrelevant.

365
00:18:25,332 --> 00:18:26,092
Mr. Song,

366
00:18:27,452 --> 00:18:29,132
if someone in business

367
00:18:29,132 --> 00:18:31,572
trips you up and leaves you reeling,

368
00:18:32,652 --> 00:18:34,252
wouldn't you retaliate

369
00:18:34,772 --> 00:18:37,172
when you recover?

370
00:18:38,132 --> 00:18:39,332
Not just retaliate.

371
00:18:40,652 --> 00:18:42,932
I'd make them pay a thousandfold.

372
00:19:01,332 --> 00:19:02,052
Mr. Song,

373
00:19:04,372 --> 00:19:05,372
since you still care,

374
00:19:05,732 --> 00:19:07,332
