375
00:19:12,132 --> 00:19:13,052
I gave her up once.

376
00:19:13,492 --> 00:19:14,932
But circumstances have changed now.

377
00:19:14,932 --> 00:19:16,132
No one in the Song family...

378
00:19:16,132 --> 00:19:17,212
That's not the point.

379
00:19:19,932 --> 00:19:21,932
Love gives you one chance.

380
00:19:25,012 --> 00:19:26,892
If you didn't help
when she needed it most,

381
00:19:28,572 --> 00:19:30,492
